event_name: Code n' Corgi: Filecoin Builders Night
description:
FIL Builders are thrilled to present Code n Corgi, a night to celebrate builders.

​Indulge in a unique fusion of authentic Bangkok street food and artisanal pizzas - because great ideas flow better with amazing food

​The evening will be packed with valuable insights from builders and plenty of opportunities for networking!

sessions.name: Registration and Welcome Drinks
sessions.description: Grab a drink, meet fellow builders, and settle in for an epic evening.

sessions.name: Kickoff
sessions.description: Let's get this event started with some high energy!

sessions.name: Keynote Speakers: Juan Benet & Molly Mackinlay
sessions.description: Hear the visionaries behind Filecoin share exclusive insights.

sessions.name: Fireside Chat with Ecosystem Builders
sessions.description: Chill conversation with the builders making waves in the space.

sessions.name: Kickstart Your Project with FILFrame
sessions.description: Get hands-on guidance to supercharge your next project!

sessions.name: Hunting ETHGlobal Filecoin Bounties
sessions.description: Learn how to snag some serious bounties and make an impact.

sessions.name: Builder Next Step Grant Announcement
sessions.description: Find out who’s getting the next big grant to level up their build.

sessions.name: Open Networking
sessions.description: Meet the coolest minds in Web3, make connections, and swap ideas!
